data.description: What a home! SUPER LOW LOT RENT of $509.49 for NEXT buyer, New metal roof with lifetime guarantee 2022 roof, new AC in 2020, new water heater and newly laid laminate! You will feel right  at home as soon as you come in, large main bedroom with big walk in closet, stack bedrooms, 2nd bedroom is a great size, new toilet recently fitted. Neutral color throughout the home. Good size kitchen with eat-in dining area, you will not be short of cabinet space either! Oversized garage, driveway is double wide - enough for 2 cars or more. The back yard is one of a kind, makes you feel like you are in a whole different world! Beautifully landscaped, with room to do so much more, patio area for grilling, no other homes behind you so you have your privacy plus rear porch that comes enclosed, fitted with an in wall AC unit to keep you cool during summer months. Adjacent to the porch is a large shed currently being used to house bikes, gutters on the exterior, home is located in the rear of the community. SO much included in the monthly fee, a private 18 hole golf course with no fees to play, 2 heated pools, pickleball, tennis, bocce, shuffleboard, gym, workshop, baseball field, arts and crafts and so much more! Water facility on site for just $278 for the whole year! Call for a showing! 55+ Community
